text: Caloria guenanti is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Caloria guenanti (Risbec, 1928). Accessed on 2018-02-17. ==Distribution== This species was described from New Caledonia. ==References== Category:Facelinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1928
title: Caloria guenanti
